@MapService_HostAddress = http://localhost:5247
@BearerToken = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Health check
GET {{MapService_HostAddress}}/health

###

### POST - Create a location
POST {{MapService_HostAddress}}/api/maps/locations
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{BearerToken}}

{
  "entityId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "entityType": "Vehicle",
  "latitude": 48.8566,
  "longitude": 2.3522,
  "address": "1 Rue de Rivoli",
  "city": "Paris",
  "country": "France"
}

###

### GET - Get location by id
GET {{MapService_HostAddress}}/api/maps/locations/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Authorization: Bearer {{BearerToken}}

###

### GET - Get location by entity
GET {{MapService_HostAddress}}/api/maps/locations/entity/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001?entityType=Vehicle
Authorization: Bearer {{BearerToken}}

###

### GET - Get my locations
GET {{MapService_HostAddress}}/api/maps/locations/my
Authorization: Bearer {{BearerToken}}

###

### GET - Get nearby locations
GET {{MapService_HostAddress}}/api/maps/locations/nearby?latitude=48.8566&longitude=2.3522&radiusKm=10&entityType=Vehicle&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{BearerToken}}

###

### PUT - Update a location
PUT {{MapService_HostAddress}}/api/maps/locations/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{BearerToken}}

{
  "latitude": 48.8600,
  "longitude": 2.3500,
  "city": "Paris",
  "isActive": true
}

###

### DELETE - Delete a location
DELETE {{MapService_HostAddress}}/api/maps/locations/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Authorization: Bearer {{BearerToken}}

###
